{
  "texts": [
    "• Maintain model accuracy: PETs should not significantly compromise the accuracy or performance of ML models.",
    "Reaching a balance between privacy and accuracy is a key challenge in PPML research.",
    "• Enable diverse data sources: PPML should allow the use of data from multiple sources while protecting data privacy.",
    "This is crucial for building robust and generalizable models.",
    "• Scalability and practicality: PPML techniques should be scalable to handle large datasets and be practically implementable in real-world applications."
  ]
}